Metric Description <code>agent_goal_accuracy</code> LLM judge: did the final output achieve the user's goal? <code>tool_call_accuracy</code> Tool sequence and argument correctness vs reference <code>tool_call_f1</code> Precision/recall for tool calls <p>Ragas metrics require a judge LLM. Set <code>JUDGE_LLM_URL</code> (and optionally <code>JUDGE_LLM_API_KEY</code>) or provide them in Metric Config:</p> <pre><code>{
  "judge_llm_url": "http://my-llm:8000/v1",
  "judge_llm_api_key": "sk-..."
}
</code></pre>
